red prior to or concomitantly with high dosages of methotrexate, such as those used to treat osteosarcoma.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/106034/', '', 'Golimumab, Cyclosporine, Ustekinumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, More', 'Fluocinolone acetonide, Fluorometholone', 1767369485);
